{"tid":286453,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"60歲既女老腦細好難頂","createTime":"2017-06-16T15:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T06:23:38.000Z","uid":66788,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fdee309cabdc4d5de649802ff37086f5c8883b50","tid":286453,"uid":66788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"叫我幫佢買飯 <br />\n叫我入好多間行既支票 又嫌我排atm 慢<br />\n又叫我管錢 <br />\npetty cash條數大過10k 又即係戒心起 比好多說話我聽<br />\n<br />\nbal 好左盤數比佢check <br />\n佢自己又bal 唔到 唔識用計數機  阻住我我收工<br />\n<br />\n自己比完單我filing <br />\n又問我做乜鳩keep 起佢張單 屈鳩我<br />\n知道自己柒  但又唔撚識點落台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 6月2 號比左信<br />\n6月30 號last day<br />\n咁宜家16 號啦 <br />\n<br />\n咁今日佢又更年期發作 <br />\n真係頂唔撚順想即走 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以後interview見到係女老腦細 即刻講粗口走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想即走 咁要唔要賠錢比公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70eed67ecaf15c96d61e5a8668859110b36f5f29","tid":286453,"uid":66788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6c27d5cc984cbb3aafdb5d11ffafcb33ff03fd94","tid":286453,"uid":33567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:32:07.000Z","msg":"還掂都走 屌佢老母"},{"pid":"aa5afcd691d6d911cf9b1a81298804dd3279f1ee","tid":286453,"uid":66788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>還掂都走 屌佢老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌完洗咪賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07e16661e2781ab492eb127dbd3160cd770084c","tid":286453,"uid":66788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:35:48.000Z","msg":"pishh"},{"pid":"94cf38d83ceabd74c303d8871295f452bb3b9195","tid":286453,"uid":21480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8adbd44630b7a93f2d7272910986336a5aa7800e","tid":286453,"uid":33567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>還掂都走 屌佢老母</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌完洗咪賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賠佢老母 佢夠膽出唔足糧勞工處見<br />\n工hea住返 吹啊"},{"pid":"2e114b848a308f2e09fa8f573091f30bd6b141ab","tid":286453,"uid":66788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>溝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比bonus 我都唔撚屌呀屌<br />\n<br />\n佢有老公生埋仔 <br />\n但老公係大陸搞生意<br />\n個仔就結左婚搬出去<br />\n屋企工人就辭職"},{"pid":"d12d04c8e3ff4c6a0e08ee068086c60e6a4bdf47","tid":286453,"uid":66788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:44:30.000Z","msg":"諗緊可唔可以咁樣<br />\n.6月糧全份糧唔要<br />\n半個月番左工<br />\n黎抵<br />\n半個月冇番工<br />\n<br />\n唔知仲洗咪賠錢 <br />\n認真想星期一唔番工"},{"pid":"d705b1b7d823fddf3aec535f3e3a9d594fc1e0e2","tid":286453,"uid":66788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:45:58.000Z","msg":"女老腦細入黎放負皮 屌你呀？"},{"pid":"bd8b85e640eb8744f821d970ae21499962161b40","tid":286453,"uid":24770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗緊可唔可以咁樣<br />\n.6月糧全份糧唔要<br />\n半個月番左工<br />\n黎抵<br />\n半個月冇番工<br />\n<br />\n唔知仲洗咪賠錢 <br />\n認真想星期一唔番工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家Hea 番算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8e71f8e33dd94121ca4c77ee84334bdd7ba0d9","tid":286453,"uid":52875,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:52:53.000Z","msg":"跟過幾個老女人做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd老女人最撚麻煩<br />\n無事化小 小事化大<br />\n睇個個都唔順眼<br />\n特別係d又後生又靚過佢<br />\n之前有個新黎既秘書同事生得幾靚<br />\n就比佢日日屌/針對<br />\n<br />\n自己做錯野就賴落d細到<br />\n叫人做野就專登講一半唔講一半<br />\n專登令你做錯  <br />\n等你做錯左/問佢 就話呢d野你唔應該問我<br />\n唔問佢 又話我地做細既唔問佢  自把自為<br />\n日日係到搬龍門<br />\n<br />\n自己outdate用埋哂d低能方法做野<br />\n人地搵到新方法 又快又準<br />\n就話人地唔聽教  逆佢意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又話我地唔受教 過份自信<br />\n我心諗&ldquo;你教都冇教啊 死臭西&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n之前跟過幾個男上司<br />\n男人講野清晰好多<br />\n真係有講過哂成個步驟點做<br />\n做錯左就真係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比佢地鬧都鬧得心甘命抵d"},{"pid":"34703a4732973393995882c8393ca8a3cdcb36d8","tid":286453,"uid":66788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T15:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前跟過幾個男上司<br />\n男人講野清晰好多<br />\n真係有講過哂成個步驟點做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個個仲撚濕鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁而家跟男上司？"},{"pid":"d8187be1ef6ce1616c213c08a62dc03a8f45a362","tid":286453,"uid":52875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:10:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前跟過幾個男上司<br />\n男人講野清晰好多<br />\n真係有講過哂成個步驟點做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個個仲撚濕鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁而家跟男上司？</blockquote><br />\n依家睇下邊個趕deadline要用人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我默默地比人認定專門做deadline fighter<br />\n<br />\n男上司要人咪跟男<br />\n女上司要人咪跟女<br />\n我地冇話fix死跟邊個<br />\n<br />\n不過全公司都知個果個女上司癲既<br />\n個個都話跟佢做野要小心d<br />\n最慘既係 個女上司特別鍾意用我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話我已經係班垃圾之中冇咁垃圾果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9592b683a493785a07600eb61cc325ed10a66e2","tid":286453,"uid":66788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:21:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n話我已經係班垃圾之中冇咁垃圾果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁講都仲係好仆街<br />\n<br />\n咁不如你做啲垃圾比佢 <br />\n等佢唔好搞你"},{"pid":"30d026b3e32fcaff456691870efd889afb8149e4","tid":286453,"uid":52875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n話我已經係班垃圾之中冇咁垃圾果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁講都仲係好仆街<br />\n<br />\n咁不如你做啲垃圾比佢 <br />\n等佢唔好搞你</blockquote><br />\n我依家邊做邊搵工<br />\n份工人工又低 又辛苦<br />\n專做埋d豬頭骨位<br />\n<br />\n想試下入d大公司做operation trainee<br />\n睇下可唔可以轉埋行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209ae17c88eed17dc9c3a5e6f80e60506d629319","tid":286453,"uid":5266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"射佢老母波喇<br />\nSL AL扣晒未"},{"pid":"4d93ba19edf46d10da1f27752251911bc8152903","tid":286453,"uid":84465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:34:46.000Z","msg":"唔駛即走嘅<br />\n返工唔做野白逗埋呢半個月啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔啱再搞冧個檔等下一手執屎"},{"pid":"3899d1a44788078c8f8f5c16e168e3def1847c10","tid":286453,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:38:44.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔關年齡事<br />\n總之女人做上司就戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n我個嫁唔出嘅上司<br />\n工事上跟佢標準無問題<br />\n但佢連做人嗰方法都要其他人跟足佢<br />\n說話方式之類嗰啲<br />\n痴撚線 <br />\n女人做上司真係慘過食屎"},{"pid":"403708bff64942b348c2fddbe8deb4ed206f7dcd","tid":286453,"uid":66788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n想試下入d大公司做operation trainee<br />\n睇下可唔可以轉埋行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁搵左幾耐 <br />\n<br />\n番緊工又要拎假in <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我secretary 轉做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />accounting"},{"pid":"3e332f81708b489bf39d886c53c9cad67e6db8fa","tid":286453,"uid":66788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>射佢老母波喇<br />\nSL AL扣晒未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最黎後個3日用左黎interview"},{"pid":"8e177bc60ebb8c58a4341edf5aab93c45d9c7a90","tid":286453,"uid":66788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔駛即走嘅<br />\n返工唔做野白逗埋呢半個月啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔啱再搞冧個檔等下一手執屎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但好難忍呀 我第時會唔會咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日佢又發癲<br />\n公司萬幾蚊進帳 我即死去入數<br />\n但佢以為我就黎走 會拎走佢啲錢<br />\n一番黎問我啲錢呢 on99"},{"pid":"ab2e922f54a4266f7792cde3ab6b5762e6ad44d3","tid":286453,"uid":66788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:54:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得唔關年齡事<br />\n總之女人做上司就戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n我個嫁唔出嘅上司<br />\n工事上跟佢標準無問題<br />\n但佢連做人嗰方法都要其他人跟足佢<br />\n說話方式之類嗰啲<br />\n痴撚線 <br />\n女人做上司真係慘過食屎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\neg 要訓練點講野先係岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣學下"},{"pid":"475905f92900c1477bbd9acc32437ffd37440d96","tid":286453,"uid":28767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T23:51:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得唔關年齡事<br />\n總之女人做上司就戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n我個嫁唔出嘅上司<br />\n工事上跟佢標準無問題<br />\n但佢連做人嗰方法都要其他人跟足佢<br />\n說話方式之類嗰啲<br />\n痴撚線 <br />\n女人做上司真係慘過食屎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\neg 要訓練點講野先係岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣學下</blockquote><br />\n唔係你諗嗰啲<br />\n係個人風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2120e6a020b643c57d0d8aa95b759d6fdf8be8","tid":286453,"uid":52875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n想試下入d大公司做op